race.comment: JAFFA'S MONELLI (6) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 27.47 beating Just A Pirate. Has a strong record from box 6, including two wins. Well placed and will be tough to beat. GOUDA MONELLI (3) shapes well for this on his handy win a few runs back, getting around this track over 488m in 27.28 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Expecting another bold showing. HE'S SUITED (1) ran a good time (30.07) when placing three back at Northam but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing seventh (28.23) at this track. Expected to do much better this time. KATITJIN (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
